parameters:
\SE[2]Even experts find it difficult to understand, so can
amateurs be of any help? \SE[3]

'Teacher: \SE[12]From now on, I will enter this child's
dream.... \.I will directly remove the lesion. \!\SE[13]I
ask for Laura- san's assistance in this.'

\SE[20]This doesn't sound like the words of a doctor....
\.We're not magicians like us either. \!\SE[3]Who are
you...?

'Teacher': \SE[37]I'm not sure if you'll believe me...
but... \SE[38]I'm not a human from this world... \SE[9]Three
years ago, I found myself in this world without realizing
it.

'Teacher': \SE[2] 'In the original world', I was studying
medicine.... \!\SE[7] I thought I could be of help in 'this
world', and before I knew it, I became known as the 'witch
doctor'....

\SE[4]I thought you looked different from us, but I guess
that's why....

\SE[4]So it was literally a different dimension of
medicine.... \.I see...\.\SE[3]That makes sense then.

\SE[76]Well... I've seen something similar before....
\SE[75]There are things like that, right...

\SE[4]Is the Teacher around the same age as Laura...?
\SE[3]What is their name?

\SE[4]Um, my name is Nagi Nakatamago. \SE[21]I think it's a
name that you're not familiar with...

\SE[16]Nakau-nagi.... \!\SE[15]It's a bit long, so let's go
with Unagi. \!\SE[1]Nice to meet you, Unagi-chan.

\SE[10]W-Wow... That's, um, rude... Vita! \SE[44]S-Sorry.
This girl tends to be quite blunt...

\SE[0]I was called that in the original world too, so I was
a little surprised. \SE[16]Please, call me that.

\SE[16]I-Is that so...!? \.Well then, nice to meet you?
\SE[3]Unagi-chan.

\SE[15]Hehe, nice to meet you. Laura-chan. Let me know when
you're ready. \SE[1]I'll be waiting here.
